        "timestamp": "2020-03-05 13:17:55.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1: Code-Review-2\n\nFirst step was to ensure renaming the legacy guard compiles correctly. I will go back to those policy types and clean them up.\n\nBut I wanted to give a show on how I'd like to clean up the guard. Similar to operational, I made a common policy that captures comment fields. And then derived from that specialized policy types per guard.\n\nI will take a look at the old guard and clean up any syntax issues with them and add description to NOT use them if possible.\n\nAgain, we'll completely remove them in Guilen Release.",
        "patchset_number": 1
      },
